Hello,


The error log claims it is a mono.dll violation, but I am using 64bit version so memory shouldn't be an issue. I have deleted various mods and it crashes shortly after finishing with modulemanager every time. I am looking for help on how to interpret this output log. I really cannot make much sense out of it, other than it crashes exactly at the same place everyime with and without Bluedog DB.  I cannot figure out the offending mod.

Below are links to the output log and my mod list. Thank you for any assistance that can be provided. All else fails, I'll just go back to 1.2.2 and forget 1.3 even exists. haha

https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B_XBruXLjI9mZ0wtbkIxYkRuVGM/view?usp=sharing (error log)
